title: PROFIenergy
description: OPC 30141: Energy Management comprises all services allowing to obtain energy related information and to control the state of all energy manageable entities contained in the Energy Information Model. The Energy Information Model is based on the PROFIenergy profile. The Energy Management functions defined in this specification are separated into three main categories: Standby Management, Energy Measurement, and Sleep Mode WOL.
